Class CarPark

  • java.lang.Object
    • CarPark

  • public class CarPark
extends java.lang.Object
    Following Java class CarPark includes and is responsible for maintaining a list of available parking spots. It also able to find a spot, add a spot, delete a spot, and provide a list of all spots included in the car park.
